<h1 id="20200319">2020/03/19</h1>
<ul>
  <li>Stock prices keep falling.</li>
  <li>Usually it leads to the increase in safe asset prices, but this time its opposite, indicating finds are collecting money to pay back their investors</li>
  <li>US plans to conduct the direct cash handout</li>
